Config::PFiles::Path
--------------------

Config::PFiles::Path manipulates the parameter file path used by IRAF
"compatible" parameter interfaces (IRAF (of course), CIAO's cxcparam,
MARX's libpfile, INTEGRAL's PIL).


INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install



DEPENDENCIES

Runtime:
    Sub::Uplevel

Build:
    Test::More

